description:
A LEGO version of how the bible depicts the world to have been created. This was a project started and finished a long time ago, and I edited it by putting better music on it. Sorry for the dodgy narration, my microphone was very quiet, so I had to speak very close to it, but with that aside, ENJOY!  

Created using a stop motion App, and edited with windows movie maker
